{"word":"G5293 - ὑποτάσσω - hypotássō - hoop-ot-as'-so - Be under obedience","slug":"G5293","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποτάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hypotássō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-ot-as'-so"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be under obedience"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C3;&#x03C9; - hupotasso&#x0304;</b> - <i>hoop-ot-as'-so</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>; to <i>subordinate</i>; reflexively to <i>obey:</i> - be under obedience (obedient), put under, subdue unto, (be, make) subject (to, unto), be (put) in subjection (to, under), submit self unto."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G1299\">G1299</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814\">G814</a>"}]}